{
  "texts": [
    "In our evaluation, the model was instructed to choose one answer from provided options.",
    "Second, the results cannot indicate the models contextual understanding and personalization aspects.",
    "The accuracy, trustworthiness, and safety of a response might be highly dependent to user's profile, medical history, and personal situation.",
    "Another limitation of this test is the lack of assessment of nutrition literacy and the clarity of the responses.",
    "Additionally, the RD exam cannot assess bias and cultural insensitivity in responses that could lead to misunderstandings or mistrust, even though generated responses are accurate."
  ]
}